## 3. Analysis Flow (`Invoke-AuditLog.ps1`)

Pure data analysis — reads source files from NAS, writes reports to local log directory. No backup, no deletion.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start: Invoke-AuditLog.ps1] --> B[Load config from ConfigPath / env var]
    B --> C[Import wecom_analysis_comm.psm1]
    C --> D[Validate dates, resolve OutputRoot, ExecutionMode]
    D --> E[Assert-TaskNameUniqueness]
    E --> F[Filter tasks by Enabled / RunMode / IncludeBU]
    F --> G{Any task selected?}

    G -- No --> H[Write run-summary with RunStatus=Success]
    H --> I[Exit 0]

    G -- Yes --> J[Loop tasks]
    J --> K[Resolve-TaskInputPath from NAS]
    K --> M{Task Type}
    M -- mail --> N[wecom_mail_analysis.ps1]
    M -- device --> O[Setup_DeviceAnalysis_Env.ps1 + wecom_devicelog_analysis.ps1]
    N --> P[Collect task result]
    O --> P
    P --> Q{More tasks?}
    Q -- Yes --> J
    Q -- No --> R{Any failed?}
    R -- Yes --> S1[Write summary: RunStatus=TasksFailed, exit 1]
    R -- No --> S2[Write summary: RunStatus=Success, exit 0]
    S2 --> LP[Write latest-run.json with RunId]
    S1 --> LP
```

### Run Artifacts

```
C:\SysAdmin\log\wecom_audit_log\runs\<RunId>\
  workflow.log
  run-summary.json
  run-summary.txt
  tasks\<task-token>\
    task.log
    report.csv
    summary.json
runs\latest-run.json
```

### Exit Codes

| Code | RunStatus | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| 0 | `Success` | All tasks passed |
| 1 | `TasksFailed` / `Failed` | At least one task failed or unhandled error |

